{"title":"寄给南征的丈夫　“只望你打到江南，再送来报功单！”","authors":["波云"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":4,"day":15}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"寄给南征的丈夫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“只望你打到江南，再送来报功单！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"波云"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日头出来红艳艳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我正在院里纺棉线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忽听街上锣鼓响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我心里说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“好象给俺送来报功单。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"话没落音成了真，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱兄弟连喊带叫跑进院："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“嫂子嫂子快去接，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"区里送来俺哥哥的报功单。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我心里又信又不信，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“进喜你又来瞎胡乱。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我正想去大街看看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妇会主任迎上前。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“先梅我来给你报个喜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你猜是送来谁的报功单？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我嘴里说：“猜不着，”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心里说：“那还不明显！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火红的太阳照满院，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喇叭锣鼓响连天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四个人抬着一块金黄匾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照眼的报功单真鲜艳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"院子平常也不算小，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那天怎的也站不开。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"里边喊着别挤啦！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"外边喊着瞧不见！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村长大声念着报功单："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“进群淮海立了功，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俘虏敌人二十名，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夺了两挺机关枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头等功臣第一名。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴掌拍的哗哗的响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"院里人人都称赞："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“咱村青年数进群，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人家真的算能干。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年轻姐妹一伙伙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叽叽咕咕围住我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这个问长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那个问短。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"故意问我："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“喜欢不喜欢？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"模范班的二牛弟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"提议叫我把话谈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树摇一枝百枝动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"院子里巴掌响连天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我还没开口红了脸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吞吞吐吐只说了半句言："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“没有共产党毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们哪有这一天！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日落西山黑了天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月亮底下再纺棉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一边纺着一边想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快把反动派来消灭完。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水连水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山连山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱穷人的血"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"相连肉相关。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江南的穷人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"受饥寒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解救他们最"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当先！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家里的活儿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有我干，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只望你打到"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江南——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再送来报功"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"单，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"报功单上再"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挂报功单！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}